00:06:09.850 --> 00:06:12.510
And if we're going to
tell relevant stories,

00:06:12.510 --> 00:06:15.840
we have to keep up to
date with both the way

00:06:15.840 --> 00:06:19.620
we talk about and
represent culture

00:06:19.620 --> 00:06:24.010
and what we know about
human social behavior.

00:06:24.010 --> 00:06:27.100
And we have to be able to
do it in a compelling way.

00:06:27.100 --> 00:06:30.690
So that's the kind of
problem that's confronting us

00:06:30.690 --> 00:06:34.380
right now, is we think about
how to transform the museum

00:06:34.380 --> 00:06:37.080
and how to repurpose
our collections.

00:06:37.080 --> 00:06:41.340
Because they are so amazing,
